{"tid":545100,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多人唔識分大家樂同大快活","createTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T14:18:07.000Z","uid":10292,"like":59,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"04047cb8f4b529c25fe39283c72c78e4c5309d60","tid":545100,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"有朝去男朋友屋企<br />\n我問佢附近有咩食，佢答我大快活<br />\n我就滿心歡喜諗住可以食大快活啲早餐<br />\n屌你原來大家樂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有次我同個frd食tea，佢話不如去大快活<br />\n個刻我心諗，正呀，佢個燒雞翼好撚好味<br />\n屌佢帶到我去之後原來係大家樂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我個朋友話，大家樂同大快活都差唔多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔！撚！喺！啩！</span><br />\n<br />\n識食嘅都知大快活早餐個牛排滑蛋再加辣肉米係完勝大家樂任何一個餐<br />\n仲有下午茶個燒雞翼串好撚好食<br />\n<br />\n唔明白點解啲人仲可以講 大家樂同大快活差唔多啫<br />\n<br />\n屌你！差好撚多呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大快活好撚正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家樂好食啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 打手"},{"pid":"e9ff31ae0499d9409f1fd8bb093ddcad9ebdf26a","tid":545100,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"好食版大家樂"},{"pid":"dc6eaf47f2406eeba70a8daa558a6ca5b6a57aa4","tid":545100,"uid":21423,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82b52b4c1635aa7f2b14b565a9706a65ddddadf3","tid":545100,"uid":41737,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ff418555bfd33e5a2317e522eea40a2562ac4b","tid":545100,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82b52b4c1635aa7f2b14b565a9706a65ddddadf3","tid":545100,"uid":41737,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cited